sentences: Makidai (stylized as MAKIDAI; born 27 October 1975, in Sakae-ku, Yokohama, Kanagawa Prefecture) is a Japanese dancer, DJ, actor and television presenter.
He is a former performer of Exile and member of PKCZ.
He is a former member of the first generation J Soul Brothers and Rather Unique.

DJ Makidai (stylized as DJ MAKIDAI) is the DJ name of the former Exile performer Makidai.

His record label is Rhythm Zone.
